					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2280344#post-2822156</guid>
				<title>They know how to swim</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2280344/scp-3850#post-2822156</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 15 May 2017 21:04:09 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>A Random Day</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1841781</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p><em>You're a floating dead boy</em><br /> <em>with nothing left to destroy</em><br /> <em>just the water in your lungs</em><br /> <em><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_5J7DFlhD5A">wished there by the ones you love</a></em></p> </blockquote> <p>A short exercise to keep my SCP-writing skills limber. Conceived within ten minutes, written up within three hours. Many thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2221240&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1515963963" alt="Taffeta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2221240)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" >Taffeta</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jekeled" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1349098&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1515963963" alt="Jekeled" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1349098)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jekeled" >Jekeled</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/twistedgears" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735681&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1515963963" alt="TwistedGears" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735681)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/twistedgears" >TwistedGears</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2887044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1515963963" alt="DrBleep" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2887044)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" >DrBleep</a></span> for review.</p> <p>Extra special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1515963963" alt="Jacob Conwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372582)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" >Jacob Conwell</a></span> for <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">being the moon of my life</span> his suggestions on improving the meat of the story, without which this would not be nearly as interesting.</p> <p>See more of my work on my <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/dr-arvind-desais-personnel-file">author page</a>!</p> 
				 	]]>
